(===============================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.1  Name of Work:) Tj T*
(     Resurfacing of Arterial Roads   BBMP East Zone \(Package 3\)) Tj T*
(     Bituminous Concrete Overlay on 12.8 km of Arterial Roads in) Tj T*
(     Mahadevapura and K.R. Puram Divisions, Bengaluru Urban District.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.2  Estimated Cost of Work:) Tj T*
(     Rs. 1,85,00,000/- \(Rupees One Crore Eighty-Five Lakh Only\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.3  Earnest Money Deposit \(EMD\):) Tj T*
(     Rs. 3,70,000/- \(Rupees Three Lakh Seventy Thousand Only\)) Tj T*
(     Payable by RTGS/NEFT or DD in favour of "Commissioner, BBMP, Bengaluru".) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.4  Tender Processing Fee: Rs. 10,000/- \(Non-refundable\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.5  Performance Security: 3% of contract value) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.6  Time for Completion: 6 months from date of commencement) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.7  Number of Covers: 2 \(Technical Bid and Financial Bid\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     Schedule of Dates:) Tj T*
(     Publication of NIT:              As published on KPPP portal) Tj T*
(     Last date for Bid Submission:    14 days from publication) Tj T*
(     Opening of Technical Bid:        16 days from publication) Tj T*
(     Bid Validity:                    180 days from submission date) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(===============================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 2   SCOPE OF WORK) Tj T*
(===============================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.1  The work involves bituminous concrete \(BC\) overlay of 12.8 km of arterial) Tj T*
(     roads in Mahadevapura and K.R. Puram divisions, including:) Tj T*
(     \(a\) Milling of existing bituminous surface) Tj T*
(     \(b\) Provision of tack coat) Tj T*
(     \(c\) Laying of Dense Bituminous Macadam \(DBM\) where required) Tj T*
(     \(d\) Bituminous Concrete \(BC\) wearing course) Tj T*
(     \(e\) Road markings and reflective studs) Tj T*
(     \(f\) Minor storm water drainage repairs as directed by Engineer-in-Charge) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2.2  All work shall conform to MORTH Specifications for Road and Bridge Works,) Tj T*
(     Fifth Revision \(latest\), and BBMP Standard Specifications.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
