(SECTION 3   ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA \(MANDATORY\)) Tj T*
(===============================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.1  TECHNICAL QUALIFICATION:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.1.1  Registration:) Tj T*
(     Bidder must be a Class I Contractor registered with Karnataka Public) Tj T*
(     Works Department \(Karnataka PWD\) or equivalent registration with) Tj T*
(     CPWD/State PWD/MES/NHAI. Registration certificate must be valid) Tj T*
(     as on date of bid submission.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.1.2  Similar Works Experience:) Tj T*
(     The bidder must have successfully completed at least 1 \(one\) similar) Tj T*
(     work during the last 5 \(five\) years ending on the last date of) Tj T*
(     submission of bids.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     "Similar work" means road construction, resurfacing, strengthening, or) Tj T*
(     widening of roads/highways of bituminous nature.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     The similar work must have a value of not less than Rs. 7,40,000/-) Tj T*
(     \(Seventy-Four Lakh Only\), i.e., 40% of estimated cost.) Tj T*
(     ) Tj T*
(     Note: Rs. 7,40,000/- = Rs. 74 Lakh = 40% of Rs. 1.85 Crore) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     Documents required:) Tj T*
(     - Work Order from the client organisation) Tj T*
(     - Completion Certificate from officer not below rank of Executive Engineer) Tj T*
(     - Performance Certificate indicating satisfactory completion) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.2  FINANCIAL QUALIFICATION:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.2.1  Annual Turnover:) Tj T*
(     Bidder shall have minimum average annual turnover of Rs. 1,00,00,000/-) Tj T*
(     \(Rupees One Crore Only\) during the last 3 financial years, certified) Tj T*
(     by a Chartered Accountant.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     Documents required:) Tj T*
(     - CA Certificate for Annual Turnover for FY 2022-23, 2023-24, 2024-25) Tj T*
(     - Audited Balance Sheets for the above years) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.3  COMPLIANCE CRITERIA:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.3.1  GST Registration: Valid GSTIN mandatory.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.3.2  PAN Card: PAN issued by Income Tax Department mandatory.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.3.3  Contractor Labour Licence: Under the Contract Labour) Tj T*
(     \(R&A\) Act, 1970, where applicable.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(     3.3.4  ISO 9001:2015 or equivalent QMS certification is preferred) Tj T*
(     but not mandatory for this tender.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
